{"metadata":{"navigatorTitle":[{"kind":"identifier","text":"simple"}],"fragments":[{"kind":"identifier","text":"simple"}],"modules":[{"name":"DotFaceCore"}],"externalID":"c:@M@DotFaceCore@objc(cs)DOTFFaceAutoCaptureConfigurationPresets(cpy)simple","role":"symbol","roleHeading":"Type Property","symbolKind":"property","title":"simple"},"kind":"symbol","hierarchy":{"paths":[["doc:\/\/DotFaceCore\/documentation\/DotFaceCore","doc:\/\/DotFaceCore\/documentation\/DotFaceCore\/DOTFFaceAutoCaptureConfigurationPresets"]]},"abstract":[{"type":"text","text":"Configuration suitable for face verification use cases."},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"The component operates without any visual aids or guidance for the user, with the exception of the detection layer (tracking circle)."},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"There is no automatic triggering of the capture process."},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"Instead, the client is responsible for initiating the capture by explicitly calling the "},{"type":"text","text":"requestCapture"},{"type":"text","text":" method."},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"This configuration provides a minimalistic approach, offering flexibility to the client in managing the capture timing and user interaction,"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"which is often desired in verification scenarios."}],"schemaVersion":{"patch":0,"minor":3,"major":0},"variants":[{"traits":[{"interfaceLanguage":"occ"}],"paths":["\/documentation\/dotfacecore\/dotffaceautocaptureconfigurationpresets\/simple"]}],"sections":[],"primaryContentSections":[{"kind":"declarations","declarations":[{"languages":["occ"],"tokens":[{"kind":"keyword","text":"@property"},{"kind":"text","text":" ("},{"kind":"keyword","text":"class"},{"kind":"text","text":", "},{"kind":"keyword","text":"nonatomic"},{"kind":"text","text":", "},{"kind":"keyword","text":"strong"},{"kind":"text","text":", "},{"kind":"keyword","text